  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.93,
    "endTime": 53.8,
    "text": "- What? - Don't try to deny it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.8,
    "endTime": 55.36,
    "text": "I've seen the whole thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.36,
    "endTime": 57.4,
    "text": "Hey, you got it all wrong! I wasn't..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.4,
    "endTime": 59.93,
    "text": "So, do you hate him more than me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.93,
    "endTime": 61.23,
    "text": "What? No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.23,
    "endTime": 63.199,
    "text": "Pete, you're the worst."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.2,
    "endTime": 66.76,
    "text": "I disliked you the moment I first laid eyes on you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.76,
    "endTime": 68.80000000000001,
    "text": "Aww, gee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.8,
    "endTime": 70.399,
    "text": "(beeping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.59,
